&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a Band 5 Staff nurse to join our enthusiastic and forward thinking busy Gynaecological ward. Stanway Ward at our Colchester Hospital site incorporates Gynaecology Emergency Admissions and our Early Pregnancy Unit. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;This is a full time (37.5 hours per week) role comprising of either day shifts (0700-1930) or night shifts (1900-0730), Monday to Sunday. For the first three months of your employment you will not be required to work weekends or night shifts, however, after this time you will be required to work a range of days, nights and weekend shifts. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;This position is for a fixed term until 31st July 2022, applications for an internal secondment would be welcomed. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Please note that this role is subject to a DBS check which will be charged to the successful candidate. Full details can be found within the &#39;DBS Information&#39; documents attached to this advert. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact: Jocel Buenaflor, Ward Sister Jocel.Buenaflor@colchesterhospital.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
